* Schema Drift\nChallenges
** What is Schema Drift
***_ Source structure changes over time
***_ New columns appear
***_ Columns removed/renamed
***_ Independent of type validation
** Delta Lake Default Behavior
***_ Schema enforcement blocks mismatches
***_ Write fails on new columns
***_ Fail-fast protects tables
** Scenarios
*** New column added
****_ Source adds phone_number
****_ Write fails, pipeline stops
*** Column removed
****_ Missing fields may cause errors
*** Column renamed
****_ Old references break
** Need for Strategy
***_ Reject it
***_ Adapt to it
***_ Preserve for later analysis
@endmindmap
